Name: UCSB
Description: College campus with amazing views. Gauchos, the home of world class staff, administration and student body

Name: Seal Beach
Description: Small beach town on the edge of North Orange County next to Long Beach California. Amazing beaches and quiet community

Name: Big Sur
Description: The lost coast of Central California. Rugged mountains meet the sea with beautiful contrast. Breath taking scenary.

Name: Lake Tahoe
Description: A crown jewel of the western United States. Sitting on the Nevada California border, Lake Tahoe is a destination for all during any season.

Name: Yosemite
Description: A beautiful National Park nestled in the Sierras. Breath taking walls of granite, gorgeous forests, and serene meadows.

Name: Trestles
Description: World class surf break. Surfers from all over the world visit to score the perfect wave.
